Product Description

Half Moon Backpack - A Quality of Backpacks

We(Half Moon) are sellers and manufacturers of various types of Customized Bags. Our product array comprises Backpacks, Sports Bags, Duffel Bags, Drawstring Bags, etc. These bags accomplish the customer's specifications and requirements. We provide these bags in numerous colors, designs, shapes, shades, patterns, etc. Our bags are known for lightweight, easy carrying, versatile usage, and durable nature.

Features

  • DURABLE MATERIAL: Made with strong polyester fabric with heavy zippers. Serves the need of a professional office laptop bag, college bag, student backpack, school bag and is suitable for all, i.e. boys, girls, men and women.
  • COMFY & STURDY: Its padded, adjustable shoulder straps do not put pressure on the shoulders. Foamed padded top handle is easy on your palm and fingers.
  • INNER MATERIAL: The material used in the inner compartments is thin yet strong and durable so, be assured of its quality. Thin material is used inside to make it lightweight & comfortable in carrying and to protect it from wear & tear.
  • LOTS OF STORAGE SPACE & POCKETS: One separate Padded laptop compartment. Multiple compartments can store lots of stuff, that too organised.
  • OTHER FEATURES: Rain cover, Reflector logo, Two water bottle/umbrella pockets, Secret-pocket at bottom for Rain cover and other stuffs, High-Quality zippers, Bartacks on pressure points for extra strength, Ergonomic design, etc.

Casual Stylish Backpack

This trendy backpack comes with multiple pockets and compartments and is very spacious and can accommodate all your stuff and will still be left with more space. With all features like padded handle, padded laptop compartment, reflector logo, bottle pockets, rain/dust cover etc, there is nothing that this backpack does not offer.

Backpack for Every Needs

This MADE IN INDIA Product features 3 large zippered compartments, 2 water bottle /umbrella pockets, Rain cover, Laptop Compartment, Top padded Handle for comfort. Its ergonomics comfortable design makes you forget the load you are carrying,

Spacious compartments

This casual backpack comes with three spacious zippered compartments which can accommodate your notebooks and other essentials with ease. Store your umbrella, notebooks and water bottle in this spacious bag and move around comfortably all day.

Comfort & Quality

This casual bag has Wide, Padded and Adjustable shoulder straps and Padded Back for comfort in carrying heavy items. Stitched properly and Bartacks on every pressure point for extra durability.

Rain / Dust Cover

This backpack includes a separate rain/dust cover which can be very handy. It keeps your valuables safe and secure from rain and dust and keeps the backpack neat and clean for a longer period of time.

Proudly Made in India

Half Moon is proud to be an Indian Brand. We understand the importance of Indian manufacturing and supply chains. It is the time when we revive local industries that's why this bag is Made in India by Indians using Indian materials.

Shipped Directly from Factory

Half Moon offers high-quality bags at the lowest prices. We offer bags directly from factory to the customer to provide the bag at lowest prices possible.
